1
00:00:58,110 --> 00:01:01,086
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,086 --> 00:01:03,056
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:03,056 --> 00:01:07,078
(Die for the One Who Understands Me)

4
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,799
Zhaoxi.

5
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:20,040
Is this all you can do for her?

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,879
Zhaoxi, you must realize

7
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,560
Father broke his earlier promise

8
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:29,400
to pass the Pavilion Master title
to Yuluo upon your marriage.

9
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,120
What else can you offer her?

10
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:33,959
And I...

11
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:37,280
I'd defy Father and reclaim
the Xuanji Pavilion for her.

12
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:38,719
And you?

13
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,519
Your sincerity is commendable.

14
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:46,599
But have you truly asked what she wants?

15
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:54,239
I'll pretend nothing happened today.

16
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,879
Wenshuang, do not bring it up again.

17
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:25,400
It's raining. The road is slippery.
Dear, be careful.

18
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,400
You don't ask where I'm going?

19
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:33,400
No matter where you go,
I will wait here for your return.

20
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,120
If I don't return tonight,

21
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,759
- you...
- I will wait here for you.

22
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,960
Where are you going?

23
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:11,120
Father, since you
haven't reversed your order,

24
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:13,319
what's the point of me staying here?

25
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:17,039
In what capacity are you asking me
to reverse the order?

26
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:20,639
You should know
she is your sister-in-law.

27
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,520
Aren't Zhaoxi's words today
warning enough?

28
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,599
So what?

29
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:30,479
Do you even know what you're doing?

30
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,120
I just don't understand.

31
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,719
You promised to give
the Xuanji Pavilion to Yuluo.

32
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:41,759
Why are you going back on your word?

33
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:45,759
Father,

34
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:48,240
since you're being unfair to Yuluo,

35
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:51,000
I'll go and seek justice for her.

36
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:03,120
(Based on Xuanwu's movements,)

37
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:06,159
(the target of his investigation
is General Shen again.)

38
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,759
(Why are the targets
of the two Heaven tasks the same?)

39
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,719
(Forget it.)

40
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,159
(Today, I just need
to disrupt Xuanwu's plan)

41
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,720
(and stop him from getting info.)

42
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:24,040
I have a small favor to ask.
General Shen, please wait.

43
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,560
(They came out in the open?)

44
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:33,639
Why do you block my way?

45
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:38,839
It's not me. It's you blocking the way.

46
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:41,279
Whose way did I block?

47
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:47,199
If you want to know, why don't you go
ask Death right now?

48
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,240
How does it feel?

49
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:54,399
You are despicable!
General, please leave!

50
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,240
He's more poisoned than you are,

51
00:04:57,240 --> 00:05:00,319
so he's cowering in the carriage.

52
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:09,879
I don't even know when I got poisoned.

53
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,319
Well played.

54
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:16,920
If I'm not mistaken,
you're from the Xuanji Pavilion?

55
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,560
You don't need to know.

56
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,480
Wait.

57
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:32,879
Why are you so anxious, my colleague?

58
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,560
You said you didn't care about my task.

59
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:38,199
Since we're both working for the Master,

60
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,199
why are you trying to stop me now?

61
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:46,040
The Pavilion never issues kill orders.

62
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,639
You've only taken on a few tasks,
so you don't understand.

63
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:54,079
Nonsense.

64
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:57,720
The Pavilion only answers to
the Master's order and task scrolls.

65
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:00,759
If you doubt me, go ask the family head.

66
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:05,439
That is, if you can stay alive to ask.

67
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:33,360
If I hadn't failed my last Heaven task,

68
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:37,480
the family head wouldn't have let you
take on the task for the Xuan Unit.

69
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,560
Poison?

70
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:54,240
It's you, young lady. Leave!

71
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:57,879
You're poisoned.
You're no match for them.

72
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,639
Don't waste your life for me.

73
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:04,040
What does it matter if you're poisoned?

74
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:06,480
You just overstepped
by taking on a Heaven task.

75
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,879
And you think you're fit
to be the Pavilion Master?

76
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:12,600
How can a member of the Earth Unit
be worthy of being my opponent?

77
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:25,839
Master.

78
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,800
Kill them!

79
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:00,000
Xuan Qing.

80
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,079
Xuan Qing.

81
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:08,000
Master, don't worry about me. Go.

82
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,160
I won't leave.

83
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,959
I disobeyed your order.

84
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:24,439
The Jiangnan estate is empty. Beware.

85
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,839
It might be a trap.

86
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:44,919
Xuan Qing, Xuan Qing!

87
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,159
Xuan Qing.

88
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,679
Xuan Qing.

89
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,720
Don't be sad.

90
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:33,000
I'll send you to her now.

91
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,519
Buddies.

92
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,399
Kill her.

93
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:11,480
Take your revenge by yourself.

94
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,120
(Soaring birds are free.)

95
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,480
(Swimming fish in the sea are free.)

96
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,639
(But there are bows
and nets in the world,)

97
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,159
(so the freedom we see before us)

98
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,399
(is only fleeting smoke.)

99
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,600
(The mundane world is a cage.)

100
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,600
In my opinion,

101
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,240
true freedom

102
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,279
is having a blade in hand.

103
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:56,080
I'm just here to complete the task.

104
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,480
I can't see what your task is.

105
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:00,360
Recently, officials
have died mysteriously.

106
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,399
I didn't know why

107
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,120
until I saw you in action today.

108
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:08,600
Turns out you're the one
working in the shadows.

109
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,480
So what if it is me?

110
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,879
That's precisely the Pavilion's task.

111
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,600
Nonsense.

112
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,279
Today,

113
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,320
I'll seek justice

114
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:23,879
for those people and Xuan Qing.

115
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:28,679
The Pavilion carries out
orders without question.

116
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:32,919
I've been searching
for a blade all my life.

117
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:45,440
But later, I came to understand...

118
00:13:18,047 --> 00:13:19,264
(Earth)

119
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:36,000
I am that blade.

120
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:42,120
The one who stirred up the Pavilion
and ordered you to kill General Shen.

121
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,440
Who is it?

122
00:13:44,559 --> 00:13:45,559
No one.

123
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:48,960
Every task I undertake
is from the Pavilion.

124
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,759
No one is directing me.

125
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,720
Then you can die.

126
00:14:06,464 --> 00:14:07,200
(Heaven)

127
00:14:31,584 --> 00:14:35,776
(Xuan Qing's Tomb)

128
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:39,200
Now, even you're gone.

129
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:44,240
(You could've been free
from these conflicts.)

130
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:49,080
At least staying by your side
was my own choice.

131
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,440
I am not like her

132
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:54,919
because I pledge my loyalty
to one person alone.

133
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,000
Gu Xuanwu is dead.

134
00:15:07,159 --> 00:15:08,440
You can rest in peace.

135
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:11,616
(Xuan Qing's Tomb)

136
00:15:12,759 --> 00:15:13,720
But don't worry.

137
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:16,440
Whoever is behind this,

138
00:15:16,559 --> 00:15:18,159
I will find them

139
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:22,120
(Xuan Qing's Tomb)
for you, for Zhaoxi,

140
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,360
but mostly for myself.

141
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:37,440
(Make General Shen Zetian
die from bandits' revenge.)

142
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:30,840
How did you...?

143
00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:35,240
I said I'd wait for you to return here.

144
00:16:57,152 --> 00:16:59,168
♪Carving a monument of longing♪

145
00:17:00,001 --> 00:17:01,888
♪For someone♪

146
00:17:01,888 --> 00:17:05,647
♪I know the past can never be relived♪

147
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:09,828
♪Life after life♪

148
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:10,920
Does it still hurt?

149
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,640
When I was injured in the past,

150
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:19,799
he used to comfort me like this.

151
00:17:21,312 --> 00:17:23,142
♪I raise my cup♪

152
00:17:24,759 --> 00:17:27,400
The injury on your neck. What happened?

153
00:17:28,704 --> 00:17:30,848
♪Tears of romance♪

154
00:17:31,238 --> 00:17:34,419
♪You smile so sadly♪

155
00:17:34,519 --> 00:17:36,640
I don't know when I got this.

156
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:42,359
Aren't you asking me
where I went tonight?

157
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:46,519
When you want to tell me, you will.

158
00:17:47,008 --> 00:17:48,878
♪I have no regrets♪

159
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:52,359
Isn't there anything you want to ask me?

160
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:54,365
♪Endless tears♪

161
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,039
There was,

162
00:17:57,119 --> 00:17:58,000
but now,

163
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,799
there's no need.

164
00:18:05,079 --> 00:18:05,799
Thank you.

165
00:18:17,519 --> 00:18:19,839
Master, the general is fine now.

166
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,079
Those assassins wore the same attire,

167
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:23,319
but...

168
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:27,480
Although they tried hard
to conceal their footwork,

169
00:18:27,799 --> 00:18:30,599
judging by their blade skills,
they seemed to be from the military.

170
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:34,160
I checked their hands,
and the calluses were very thick.

171
00:18:35,319 --> 00:18:36,160
The barracks.

172
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:39,160
Go to the army and check

173
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:42,039
if anyone has recently died,
gone missing or taken leave.

174
00:18:42,559 --> 00:18:44,839
Follow these leads.

175
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:46,380
Yes.

176
00:18:48,279 --> 00:18:51,079
Her guard didn't leave in anger that day

177
00:18:51,599 --> 00:18:53,519
but hurriedly rode away and back.

178
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:56,119
She was so loyal.

179
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:59,039
But she visited
the old house in Jiangnan.

180
00:18:59,279 --> 00:19:02,359
I wonder if she reported
something unfavorable against you.

181
00:19:07,839 --> 00:19:10,880
You left under the guise of death
and refused to return to the palace.

182
00:19:11,319 --> 00:19:12,920
Was it all for that woman?

183
00:19:14,319 --> 00:19:15,960
I've seen her in Suzhou.

184
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,400
She's from the Xuanji Pavilion.

185
00:19:19,079 --> 00:19:22,160
If that's the case,
we mustn't let her leave.

186
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:24,400
No matter.

187
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,960
After the assassination,
I followed the clues to the Gu family

188
00:19:28,039 --> 00:19:29,079
and stayed to investigate.

189
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,799
If the Pavilion is really behind this,

190
00:19:32,279 --> 00:19:35,119
it is actually the safest place now.

191
00:19:36,079 --> 00:19:37,279
Just because of that?

192
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:41,880
The newly deceased Gu Zhaoxi
looked remarkably like me.

193
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,799
Upon investigation,

194
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:47,920
he turned out to be my brother, Yin Ci,
whom we all believed died years ago.

195
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:49,799
How could it be?

196
00:19:50,519 --> 00:19:52,839
"Newly deceased?" He's already...?

197
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:58,759
Was the assassin
back then really Gu Jiang?

198
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:02,480
What exactly happened?

199
00:20:35,998 --> 00:20:41,061
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

200
00:20:41,598 --> 00:20:46,919
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

201
00:20:47,486 --> 00:20:54,114
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

202
00:20:54,114 --> 00:20:58,878
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

203
00:20:58,878 --> 00:21:01,214
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

204
00:21:01,214 --> 00:21:07,914
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

205
00:21:07,914 --> 00:21:14,686
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

206
00:21:14,686 --> 00:21:21,822
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

207
00:21:21,822 --> 00:21:26,206
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

208
00:21:26,206 --> 00:21:28,830
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

209
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:35,464
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

210
00:21:35,464 --> 00:21:42,014
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

211
00:21:42,014 --> 00:21:49,138
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

212
00:21:49,228 --> 00:21:53,598
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

213
00:21:53,598 --> 00:21:56,306
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

214
00:21:56,306 --> 00:22:02,206
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

215
00:22:02,846 --> 00:22:08,834
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
